               <h4 class="alert-heading d-flex align-items-center">
                  <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
                  Critical Updates Notice
               </h4>
               <hr>
               <p class="mb-0">
                  Occasionally, critical updates may be released and should be downloaded directly from the 
                  <a href="https://github.com/war100ck/Server-Api-BnS-2017" target="_blank" class="alert-link">GitHub repository</a>.
                  These updates can alter the file structure or paths, potentially affecting the functionality of the BnS API server.
