                  <li>Check forum for update details before applying</li>
                  <li>Critical updates may require manual installation</li>
                  <li>Review file structure changes after major updates</li>
               </ul>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-info" data-bs-dismiss="modal">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-1"></i> Understood
